articles.author: Jesse Sarles
articles.title: Miss Colorado, 2nd Lt. Madison Marsh, crowned Miss America 2024 - CBS News
articles.description: Madison Marsh, 22, is a second lieutenant in the U.S. Air Force and the first-ever active duty servicemember to win the Miss America title.
